title: Bug 116564 - Hyperlink builder title changes with settings
OB: When clicking on 'OK' and then reopening the hyperlink builder, the title of the hyperlink builder changes to 'www.actuate.com'.
EB: The title of the hyperlink builder should be 'Hyperlink Options' instead of 'www.actuate.com'.
SR: To reproduce the issue: Set a label hyperlink as 'www.actuate.com', then reopen the hyperlink builder.
